text: Société Tunisienne de l'Air, or Tunisair () is the flag carrier airline of Tunisia. Formed in 1948, it operates scheduled international services to European, African and Middle Eastern destinations. Its main base is Tunis- Carthage International Airport. The airline's head office is in Tunis, near Tunis Airport."Tunisair Tunis." Tunisair. Retrieved on 21 June 2010.
